                            <div class="flex-grow-1">
                                <h6 class="heading-6 font-weight-semibold clr-text margin-bottom-3">
                                Where you can live in Canada
                                </h6>
                                <p class="clr-text margin-bottom-5">
                                <ul>
                                <li>When you fill out your profile, we’ll ask you where you plan to live in Canada.</li>
                                <li>The province has its own rules for choosing immigrants who will adapt well to living there.</li>
                                <li>If the Province chooses you and gives you a CSQ, you must apply to Immigration, Refugees and Citizenship Canada for PR.</li>
                                </ul> 
                                </p>
